org.mobicents.slee.container.profile.entity
Interface ProfileEntityFramework

All Known Implementing Classes:
JPAProfileEntityFramework
public interface ProfileEntityFramework

A profile entity framework is responsible to implement concrete details about profile entity management, including class generation, persistent data storage, query parsing, etc.

Author:
martins
